root="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:anchor>937</fr:anchor><fr:taxon>Proposition</fr:taxon><fr:addr>fga1-proposition-5</fr:addr><fr:route>fga1-proposition-5.xml</fr:route><fr:number>5</fr:number><fr:parent>fga1-3</fr:parent></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>
    Let <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> be a non-singular algebraic variety of dimension <fr:tex>n</fr:tex>, and let <fr:tex>Y</fr:tex> be an algebraic subset of dimension <fr:tex>q=n-p</fr:tex> of <fr:tex>X</fr:tex>.
    Let <fr:tex>\mathscr { F }</fr:tex> be a coherent algebraic sheaf on <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> with support contained in <fr:tex>Y</fr:tex>, and let <fr:tex>\mathscr { L }</fr:tex> be a locally-free algebraic sheaf on <fr:tex>X</fr:tex>.
    Then the sheaves <fr:tex>\mathscr {E} \kern  -1.5pt \mathit {xt} _{ \mathcal {O} _X}^i( \mathscr { F } , \mathscr { L } )</fr:tex> are zero for <fr:tex>i&lt;p</fr:tex>, and, when <fr:tex>i=p</fr:tex>, there is a canonical isomorphism

    <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
toc="true"
numbered="false"
show-heading="true"
show-metadata="false"
expanded="true"
root="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:anchor>716</fr:anchor><fr:taxon>Equation</fr:taxon><fr:addr>fga1-equation-3.7</fr:addr><fr:route>fga1-equation-3.7.xml</fr:route><fr:number>3.7</fr:number><fr:parent>fga1-proposition-5</fr:parent></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:tex
display="block">          \mathscr {E} \kern  -1.5pt \mathit {xt} _{ \mathcal {O} _X}^p( \mathscr { F } , \mathscr { L } )         =  \mathscr {H} \kern  -2.5pt \mathit {om} _{ \mathcal {O} _X}( \mathscr { F } , \mathscr {E} \kern  -1.5pt \mathit {xt} ^p( \mathcal {O} _X/ \mathfrak {J}, \mathscr { L } ))       \tag{3.7}       </fr:tex></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>

    where <fr:tex>\mathfrak {J}</fr:tex> denotes an arbitrary sheaf of ideals on <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> that annihilates <fr:tex>\mathscr { F }</fr:tex> and has <fr:tex>Y</fr:tex> as its set of zeros.
    In particular, if <fr:tex>\mathscr { F }</fr:tex> is a coherent algebraic sheaf on <fr:tex>Y</fr:tex>, then

    <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
toc="true"
numbered="false"
show-heading="true"
